{"word":"H6118 - עֵקֶב - ʻêqeb - ay'-keb - [idiom] because","slug":"H6118","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">עֵקֶב</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>ʻêqeb"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>ay'-keb"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>[idiom] because"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E2;&#x05E7;&#x05D1; - &#x201B;e&#x0302;qeb</b> - <i>ay'-keb</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H6117\">H6117</a> in the sense of <a href=\"#/H6119\">H6119</a>; a <i>heel</i>, that is, (figuratively) the <i>last</i> of anything (used adverbially <i>for ever</i>); also <i>result</i>, that is, <i>compensation</i>; and so (adverbially with preposition or relatively) on <i>account</i> of: -  X because, by, end, for, if, reward."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3290\">H3290</a>, <a href=\"#/H3291\">H3291</a>, <a href=\"#/H6117\">H6117</a>, <a href=\"#/H6119\">H6119</a>, <a href=\"#/H6120\">H6120</a>, <a href=\"#/H6121\">H6121</a>, <a href=\"#/H6122\">H6122</a>, <a href=\"#/H6126\">H6126</a>"}]}